{"tid":619454,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[有圖]17-18 LIHKG香港冠軍女神聯賽第30輪投選專區 #文詠珊 陳法拉 沈卓盈 岑麗香 袁澧林 陳嘉寶","createTime":"2018-04-06T15:59:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-07T15:55:03.000Z","uid":92376,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7e3f713d3cf7b88021e65c6471bb3dc7583a8173","tid":619454,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T15:59:26.000Z","msg":"以下為即將舉行之賽事<br />\n會員可留意稍後時間發出的比賽專用回覆並以回覆評分功能進行投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(唔識點樣用回覆評分功能黎投票既巴打可以參考下面既教學)<br />\n<br />\n由首場12:00am開始,每兩分鐘開賽一場<br />\n<br />\n黃心美v袁澧林<br />\n莊錠欣v簡幗儀<br />\n岑麗香v孫慧雪<br />\n文詠珊v鄧麗欣<br />\n劉佩玥v麥美恩<br />\n林泳淘v沈卓盈<br />\n彭慧中v陳煒<br />\n黃翠如v陳法拉<br />\n陳嘉寶v黃心穎<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/hiNda68.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FhiNda68.png&h=d4221617&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/s2sfX8L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fs2sfX8L.png&h=b53ffa65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n冠聯第二十九輪積分榜<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/SSCfoFE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FSSCfoFE.png&h=12162d4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://i.imgur.com/fg4vwe7.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Ffg4vwe7.png&d=OJlPO1j1NBv%2FxoQriCu%2BAv%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=83e3ea03\" target=\"_blank\">http://i.imgur.com/fg4vwe7.png</a><br />\n有關主場指定額外得分情況,請參閱主場額外分數增幅表<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dc1e23df37ed120f5bd69017915d9aff3bd5b2d","tid":619454,"uid":92376,"like":24,"dislike":155,"score":-131,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T16:00:00.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2017-18 LIHKG香港冠軍女神聯賽第三十輪</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">*括號內數字為聯賽排名</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2018-4-7 12am-10pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/PGitLqT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FPGitLqT.png&h=407eae36&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/rYeiDIq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FrYeiDIq.png&h=75553268&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">(18)黃心美vs袁澧林(5)</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">聯賽賽時為22小時，會員可於本回覆發起後22小時內於以回覆評分功能(前者上箭咀;後者下箭咀)投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的回覆評分功能投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">主場女神票數達到15者會按得票相關情況獲得指定額外分數，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},{"pid":"af36881c1ec2cca3eccd57a7cea4036d2786130f","tid":619454,"uid":92376,"like":89,"dislike":69,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T16:02:00.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2018-4-7 12:02am-10:02pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/kXWjbxb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FkXWjbxb.png&h=88ea7795&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/ZFz9SGc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FZFz9SGc.png&h=2d03ff95&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">(12)莊錠欣vs簡幗儀(15)</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">聯賽賽時為22小時，會員可於本回覆發起後22小時內於以回覆評分功能(前者上箭咀;後者下箭咀)投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的回覆評分功能投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">主場女神票數達到15者會按得票相關情況獲得指定額外分數，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},{"pid":"4070880c58ac3b6e08671c53c7af838692cc238c","tid":619454,"uid":92376,"like":108,"dislike":74,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2